7.32	The_Minus_Man	The Minus Man	The Minus Man is a 1999 film based on the novel by Lew McCreary. It was directed by Hampton Fancher, who also wrote the screenplay. The film centers on a psychotic killer whom Fancher describes as "a cross between Psycho's Norman Bates, Melville's Billy Budd and Being There's Chauncey Gardner".	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/20/Minus_man_ver2.jpg/220px-Minus_man_ver2.jpg
